data.description: A sweet entry into the thriving and growing town of West Orange. This 3 bedroom offers cozy bedrooms on level 2 with added space in level one including a rear office area and enclosed back porch. Appreciate the new furnace, private driveway and gated backyard space. Bring your fresh ideas and a few tools to touch up some parts of this AS IS sale.
